cassonne</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Notre-Dame_de_Reims" title="Notre-Dame de Reims" class="mw-redirect">Cathedral of Notre-Dame</a>, former <a href="/wiki/Abbey_of_Saint-Remi" title="Abbey of Saint-Remi">Abbey of Saint-Remi</a>&#160;<small>and</small> <a href="/wiki/Palace_of_Tau" title="Palace of Tau">Palace of Tau</a>, <a href="/wiki/Reims" title="Reims">Reims</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Cathedral_of_Chartres" title="Cathedral of Chartres" class="mw-redirect">Cathedral of Chartres</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <small>Cistercian</small>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Abbey_of_Fontenay" title="Abbey of Fontenay">Abbey of Fontenay</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Fortifications_of_Vauban" title="Fortifications of Vauban">Fortifications of Vauban</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Le_Havre" title="Le Havre">Le Havre</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Loire_Valley" title="Loire Valley">Loire Valley</a>&#160;<small>between Sully-sur-Loire&#160;and Chalonnes</small><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Lyon" title="Lyon">Lyon</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Mont_Saint-Michel" title="Mont Saint-Michel">Mont Saint-Michel</a>&#160;<small>and its Bay</small><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/New_Caledonia_Barrier_Reef" title="New Caledonia Barrier Reef">Lagoons of New Caledonia: Reef Diversity and Associated Ecosystems</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Ch%C3%A2teau_de_Fontainebleau" title="Château de Fontainebleau" class="mw-redirect">Fontainebleau Palace</a>&#160;<small>and</small> <a href="/wiki/Fontainebleau#Fontainebleau_forest" title="Fontainebleau">Park</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <strong class="selflink">Palace and Park of Versailles</strong><span style="font-